# SafeVoice frontend configuration.
#
# This is a privacy-first whistleblower portal. It MUST NOT send report content,
# evidence, or reporter data to any third-party AI service or any host outside the
# EEA (see SafeVoice/docs/compliance/06-SECURITY-DATA-PROTECTION.md and CLAUDE.md §3).

# Active jurisdiction (ISO 3166-1 alpha-2). Drives controller name, external
# reporting authority, retention period, deletion windows, and default language.
# Defaults to "PL" (Poland). Other EU states are added in src/config/jurisdictions.ts.
VITE_SAFEVOICE_JURISDICTION="PL"
